About me

Hi there! I'm Amit, passionate and experienced MERN (MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, Node.js) Full Stack Developer dedicated to building scalable, user-friendly, and high-performance web applications. With a strong foundation in modern web technologies, I specialize in crafting efficient solutions tailored to meet business needs.

Design and implement responsive, dynamic user interfaces using React.js. My toolkit includes hooks, state management, and advanced styling with CSS, SCSS, and frameworks like Material-UI. I create robust RESTful APIs and real-time services with Node.js and Express.js, ensuring seamless integration with MongoDB for database management.

So if you're in need of a new website or just looking to revamp your current online presence, I'd love to chat and see how I can help. Let's bring your website dreams to reality together!
